                <head>No. 798<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On May 9, the Governments of the United States, the United Kingdom, and France
                    sent a joint note to the Soviet Foreign Ministry requesting a reply to their
                    tripartite note of March 13 which included the proposed text of the draft
                    abbreviated treaty. For text of this note of May 9, see Department of State <hi
                        rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, May 19, 1952, page 778.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
